name: Terminated (PC title)
blurb: Terminated is a first-person moba for the PC that puts you in control of the action without the RTS gameplay.

rewards.reward:
Name in the Credits:

We believe every bit of support should not only be appreciated but acknowledged. Pledging $1 will get your name on the credits of the game and a personal thank you from us here in LP Studios.
If we have hundreds of pledges, then get ready for a long list of credits.

Name in the Credits, 3 special Terminated wallpapers with personalized resolution, and a beta invite:\r\n\r\nThis support has your name on the list of credits and it also gets you 3 Terminated wallpapers with your proper resolution sent personally to your email. Your wallpaper will contain fresh screenshots with updated models and textures that we wont put up on the internet. You'll be the first to see it and the first to have it. You will also have access to the early beta and all the updates/patches until the game's full release.

All previous pledges 
+
Purchasing your digital copy with access to the early beta versions of the game:

Not only are you buying a copy of the game that will be immediately available to you the day it's released, but you'll also have access to the early beta of the game. As soon as we have a playable version ready, you'll be ready to play it and continue playing it with the updates and patches until the game is fully finished.

A pledge of this amount gets you 2 copies of the game available to you upon release with 2 invites for the beta that will be playable until the game is fully released. As well as all the other perks above.

3 copies of the game with 3 beta invites, the rest of the above, and a Q&A session with the dev team where you can ask any questions about the game and a sneak peek of the progress being made. You'll be contacted through email.

Name in the credits, 3 unique wallpapers, 4 copies of the game with 4 beta invites, an invite to the Q&A sessions with the devs, and the chance to get your own custom character skin in as part of customization. Just draw up your design (even if you're not that great with drawing) and we'll make it look as awesome as what you've got visualized.

Name in the credits, 3 unique wallpapers, 4 copies of the game with 4 beta invites, an invite to the Q&A sessions with the devs, your own custom character skin, and being able to create one ability set ingame. We'll discuss what you'd like to see, the effect, the power, and make sure it's balanced and fits the game well enough to be put in.

Name in the credits, 3 unique wallpapers, 4 copies of the game with 4 beta invites, an invite to the Q&A sessions with the devs, your own custom character skin, your own custom ability set, and a chance to put in your own gametype in the game. \r\nAgain, the devs will work this out with you so we can ensure that the gametype will not only be fun, but that it will be worth the time to make it. The more people here, the more gametypes we'll have on top of what we already have planned.

All of the right above and a being able to work with the dev team for creating a custom voice set that will be used for character customization. We'll have a day or two dedicated for voice acting with the people pledging this amount to get your sexy voice ingame for the rest of the world to hear.
